<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Restaurant is Ready!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #FF6B35;
            padding-bottom: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #FF6B35;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .header p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 10px 0 0 0;
        }
        .success-banner {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4CAF50 0%, #45a049 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 25px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.3);
        }
        .success-banner h2 {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: white;
        }
        .success-banner p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }
        .menu-link-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 25px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
        }
        .menu-link-section h3 {
            margin: 0 0 20px 0;
            font-size: 22px;
            color: white;
        }
        .menu-link-box {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border: 2px dashed rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        .menu-link {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: white;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: block;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .copy-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 15px 10px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .copy-button:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .dashboard-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B35 0%, #f7931e 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 25px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.3);
        }
        .dashboard-section h3 {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: white;
        }
        .dashboard-section p {
            margin: 0 0 20px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }
        .dashboard-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .dashboard-button:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .restaurant-info {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f8ff 0%, #e6f3ff 100%);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #2196F3;
        }
        .restaurant-info h3 {
            color: #1976d2;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .info-item {
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 3px solid #2196F3;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .info-item strong {
            color: #1976d2;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        .info-item p {
            margin: 8px 0 0 0;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .instructions {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f5e8 0%, #f1f8e9 100%);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        .instructions h3 {
            color: #2e7d32;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .instructions ol {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding-left: 25px;
        }
        .instructions li {
            margin: 12px 0;
            color: #1b5e20;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .instructions strong {
            color: #2e7d32;
        }
        .qr-access-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3e0 0%, #ffe0b2 100%);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #ff9800;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .qr-access-section h3 {
            color: #e65100;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .qr-access-section p {
            color: #bf360c;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .dashboard-location {
            background: white;
            border: 2px dashed #ff9800;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .dashboard-location h4 {
            color: #e65100;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .dashboard-location p {
            color: #bf360c;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .pro-tips {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f3e5f5 0%, #e1bee7 100%);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #9c27b0;
        }
        .pro-tips h3 {
            color: #7b1fa2;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .pro-tips ul {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding-left: 25px;
        }
        .pro-tips li {
            margin: 12px 0;
            color: #6a1b9a;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 35px;
            padding-top: 25px;
            border-top: 2px solid #ddd;
            color: #666;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 8px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .highlight-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff8e1 0%, #ffecb3 100%);
            border: 2px solid #ffc107;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .highlight-box h4 {
            color: #f57c00;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .highlight-box p {
            color: #e65100;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üéâ Your Restaurant is Ready!</h1>
            <p>Welcome to the digital future of dining!</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Success Banner -->
        <div class="success-banner">
            <h2>‚úÖ Restaurant Successfully Created!</h2>
            <p>Your restaurant "<strong><%= restaurantName %></strong>" is now live and ready to accept digital orders.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Menu Link Section -->
        <div class="menu-link-section">
            <h3>üîó Your Digital Menu Link</h3>
            <p>Share this link with your customers to access your digital menu:</p>
            
            <div class="menu-link-box">
                <span class="menu-link">
                    <%= (process.env.FRONTEND_URL || process.env.VITE_FRONTEND_URL || 'http://localhost:5173') %>/menu/<%= restaurant._id %>
                </span>
            </div>
            
            <p><strong>üí° Pro Tip:</strong> Customers can simply click this link or type it in their browser to access your menu!</p>
            
            <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
                <a href="<%= (process.env.FRONTEND_URL || process.env.VITE_FRONTEND_URL || 'http://localhost:5173') %>/menu/<%= restaurant._id %>" target="_blank" class="copy-button">
                    üåê Open Menu
                </a>
                <button onclick="copyToClipboard('<%= (process.env.FRONTEND_URL || process.env.VITE_FRONTEND_URL || 'http://localhost:5173') %>/menu/<%= restaurant._id %>')" class="copy-button">
                    üìã Copy Link
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Dashboard Access Section -->
        <div class="dashboard-section">
            <h3>üì± QR Code & Dashboard Access</h3>
            <p>Your QR code is now available in your dashboard! Here's how to access it:</p>
            
            <a href="<%= (process.env.FRONTEND_URL || process.env.VITE_FRONTEND_URL || 'http://localhost:5173') %>/dashboard" target="_blank" class="dashboard-button">
                üöÄ Go to Dashboard
            </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Restaurant Information -->
        <div class="restaurant-info">
            <h3>üìç Restaurant Details</h3>
            <div class="info-grid">
                <div class="info-item">
                    <strong>Restaurant Name</strong>
                    <p><%= restaurantName %></p>
                </div>
                <% if (restaurantAddress) { %>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <strong>Address</strong>
                        <p><%= restaurantAddress %></p>
                    </div>
                <% } %>
                <% if (restaurantPhone) { %>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <strong>Phone Number</strong>
                        <p><%= restaurantPhone %></p>
                    </div>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- How It Works -->
        <div class="instructions">
            <h3>üöÄ How Your Digital Menu Works</h3>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Share the Link:</strong> Send the menu link to customers via email, social media, or messaging apps</li>
                <li><strong>Customers Browse:</strong> They can view your full menu with prices, descriptions, and images</li>
                <li><strong>Place Orders:</strong> Customers can order directly from their phones</li>
                <li><strong>Real-time Updates:</strong> Orders appear instantly in your dashboard</li>
                <li><strong>Manage Orders:</strong> Update status, track deliveries, and manage everything from your dashboard</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <!-- QR Code Access Information -->
        <div class="qr-access-section">
            <h3>üì± QR Code Access</h3>
            <p><strong>Your QR code is ready and available in your dashboard!</strong></p>
            
            <div class="dashboard-location">
                <h4>üìç Where to Find Your QR Code</h4>
                <p><strong>Dashboard ‚Üí Create Restaurant Section</strong></p>
                <p>Your QR code is displayed prominently with download and print options</p>
                <p>You can also find it in the main Dashboard page</p>
            </div>
            
            <p><strong>üí° Pro Tip:</strong> The QR code in your dashboard is high-quality and ready for printing at any size!</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Pro Tips -->
        <div class="pro-tips">
            <h3>üí° Pro Tips for Success</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Share the Link:</strong> Include the menu link in your social media bio, website, and email signatures</li>
                <li><strong>Print QR Codes:</strong> Download and print QR codes from your dashboard to display on tables and walls</li>
                <li><strong>Train Staff:</strong> Make sure your team knows about the digital menu and can guide customers</li>
                <li><strong>Update Regularly:</strong> Keep your menu items, prices, and availability current</li>
                <li><strong>Monitor Orders:</strong> Check your dashboard regularly for new orders and updates</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Quick Actions Highlight -->
        <div class="highlight-box">
            <h4>‚ö° Quick Actions Available in Your Dashboard</h4>
            <p>‚Ä¢ Create Categories ‚Ä¢ Add Menu Items ‚Ä¢ Manage Orders ‚Ä¢ View Analytics ‚Ä¢ Live Order Monitoring</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>üéâ Congratulations!</strong> Your restaurant is now part of the digital dining revolution!</p>
            <p>Need help? Your QR code and all tools are available in your dashboard.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #999;">
                This email was sent because you created a restaurant on ZinR. 
                You can manage all settings from your dashboard.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function copyToClipboard(text) {
            navigator.clipboard.writeText(text).then(function() {
                alert('Menu link copied to clipboard!');
            }, function(err) {
                console.error('Could not copy text: ', err);
            });
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
